headline: EQT announces accretive acquisition of certain assets from Olympus Energy
summary: The Company has entered into a purchase agreement with Olympus Energy Holdings Hyperion Midstream and Bow & Arrow Land Company, collectively, Olympus Energy, pursuant to which the Company has agreed to acquire the upstream and midstream assets of Olympus Energy for total consideration of $1.8B.
